obj_root_law_sections_14_content:
  string
  line 14
  line `1 [ THE FIRST SCHEDULE ]`
  line `[ See s ection 2( i )]`
  line `1. Fruits, vegetables and their products.`
  line `2. Meat and meat products.`
  line `3. Poultry and poultry products.`
  line `4. Dairy products.`
  line `5. Confectionary, biscuits and bakery products.`
  line `6. Honey, jaggery and sugar products.`
  line `7. Cocoa and its products, chocolates of all kinds.`
  line `8. Alcoholic and non - alcoholic beverages.`
  line `9. Cereal products.`
  line `10. Cashewnuts, groundnuts, peanuts and walnuts.`
  line `11. Pickles, chutneys and papads.`
  line `12. Guar Gum.`
  line `13. Floriculture and floriculture products.`
  line `14. Herbal and medicinal plants.`
  line `2 [15. De - oiled rice bran.]`
  line `1. The Schedule numbered as the First Schedule by Act 20 of 2009, s. 8 (w.e.f. 13 - 10 - 2008).`
  line `2. Added by Notification No. S.O. 2100(E) ( dated 5 th M ay, 2022).`
